a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g"><span title="Introduction" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Introduction</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/specification"><span title="Specification" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Specification</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link menu__link--active" aria-current="page" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/led-indications"><span title="LED Indications" class="linkLabel_WmDU">LED Indications</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/configuration"><span title="Configuration" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Configuration</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/attaching-to-drone"><span title="Attaching to the Drone" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Attaching to the Drone</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/battery-charging"><span title="Battery Charging" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Battery Charging</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/firmware-update"><span title="Firmware Update" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Firmware Update</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/safety-notices"><span title="Safety Notices" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Safety Notices</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/limited-warranty"><span title="Limited Warranty" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Limited Warranty</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/maintenance"><span title="Maintenance" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Maintenance</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/troubleshooting"><span title="Troubleshooting" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Troubleshooting</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/downloads"><span title="Downloads" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Downloads</span></a></li><li class="theme-doc-sidebar-item-link theme-doc-sidebar-item-link-level-1 menu__list-item"><a class="menu__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/firmware-changelog"><span title="Firmware Changelog" class="linkLabel_WmDU">Firmware Changelog</span></a></li></ul></nav></div></div></aside><main class="docMainContainer_TBSr"><div class="container padding-top--md padding-bottom--lg" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="row" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="col docItemCol_VOVn" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="docItemContainer_Djhp" bis_skin_checked="1"><article><nav class="theme-doc-breadcrumbs breadcrumbsContainer_Alpn" aria-label="Breadcrumbs"><ul class="breadcrumbs" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList"><li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a aria-label="Home page" class="breadcrumbs__link" href="https://help.dronetag.com/"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="breadcrumbHomeIcon_xK9p"><path d="M10 19v-5h4v5c0 .55.45 1 1 1h3c.55 0 1-.45 1-1v-7h1.7c.46 0 .68-.57.33-.87L12.67 3.6c-.38-.34-.96-.34-1.34 0l-8.36 7.53c-.34.3-.13.87.33.87H5v7c0 .55.45 1 1 1h3c.55 0 1-.45 1-1z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></a></li><li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a class="breadcrumbs__link" itemprop="item" href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g"><span itemprop="name">Dronetag Mini 4G</span></a><meta itemprop="position" content="2"></li><li itemscope="" itemprop="itemListElement" itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem" class="breadcrumbs__item breadcrumbs__item--active"><span class="breadcrumbs__link" itemprop="name">LED Indications</span><meta itemprop="position" content="1"></li></ul></nav><div class="tocCollapsible_ETCw theme-doc-toc-mobile tocMobile_ITEo" bis_skin_checked="1"><button type="button" class="clean-btn tocCollapsibleButton_TO0P">On this page</button></div><div class="theme-doc-markdown markdown" bis_skin_checked="1"><header><h1>LED Indications</h1></header>
<p>Three LEDs indicate the status of the device and its components - Positioning (GNSS), Remote ID (RID) and Status (STAT).</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>Positioning (GNSS)</strong> informs about the current state of the satellite positioning system.</li>
<li class=""><strong>Remote ID (RID)</strong> informs about everything related to the Network &amp; Direct Remote ID functionality.</li>
<li class=""><strong>Status (STAT)</strong> informs about the overall device status.</li>
</ul>
<iframe width="100%" height="315" src="./LED Indications _ Dronetag Help_files/NtR4JV6A8_c.html" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" bis_size="{&quot;x&quot;:470,&quot;y&quot;:348,&quot;w&quot;:937,&quot;h&quot;:315,&quot;abs_x&quot;:470,&quot;abs_y&quot;:348}" bis_id="fr_75ekq06n1mcafej4elomzu" bis_depth="0" bis_chainid="2"></iframe>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="device-states">Device States<a href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini-4g/led-indications/#device-states" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>Possible states are following:</p>
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt blue_wgce pulsing_nFd9" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt blue_wgce undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt blue_wgce undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Charging</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">Blue gradually pulsing on all indicators</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>The number of non-pulsing LEDs shows the current battery charge. E.g 50% charged, 1 solid and 1 pulsing blue LEDs, 100% charged = 3 solid blue LEDs. Battery charge can be briefly checked by short pressing the button once while turned off.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt yellow_FVmI pulsing_nFd9" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Waiting for Component</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">One or more indicators are pulsing yellow</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>Yellow means that the pulsing component is not ready for a flight or has a temporary outage. Wait for the component to get ready (green). In cases of poor signal, move to an area with better coverage. Find more information about this subject in <a href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini/troubleshooting">Troubleshooting</a>.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Flight is Ready to Start</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">All indicators are green lit</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>In this state, the device is ready for the flight to be started. Do the short press of the button to&nbsp;start your flight.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN running_1_iFRX" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN running_2_UpqZ" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN running_3_Hw15" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Dronetag Cloud Communication</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">Running green on all indicators</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>For the proper function of Network Remote ID, each flight needs to be successfully created and then ended on our cloud. It is indicated by running green LEDs (please keep in mind this may take some time). The communication may fail due to a poor cellular signal or internal error on&nbsp;the&nbsp;server-side. In this case, the device might end up in an error state end then it needs to be restarted.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt white_tszl double-flashing_C8cd" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt white_tszl double-flashing_C8cd" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt white_tszl double-flashing_C8cd" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Device in Flight</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">Flashing white on one or more indicators</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>In this state, the device sends the Network Remote ID data to our cloud and broadcasts Direct Remote ID data to everyone around via Bluetooth. The particular Remote ID technology is defined in the <a href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini/configuration">Configuration </a>and cannot be changed during the flight.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt yellow_FVmI pulsing_nFd9" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt white_tszl double-flashing_C8cd" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt white_tszl double-flashing_C8cd" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Device in flight - Warning</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">Flashing white on STAT and pulsing yellow on RID/GNSS</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>GNSS or RID (or both) can have a temporary outage (e.g. lost GNSS or weak LTE). This will be indicated by pulsing a yellow LED on a component that is affected. <strong>Please note that Remote ID data cannot be refreshed in this state.</strong></p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt white_tszl double-flashing_C8cd" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt red_gEJV undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt white_tszl double-flashing_C8cd" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Device in flight - Cloud Communication Error</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">STAT and GNSS indicators are flashing white, RID indicator is red lit</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>If cloud communication fails during flight, the flight continues without interruption. This condition is indicated by a solid red RID indicator.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN unavailable_ok_zUDw" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt yellow_FVmI unavailable_nok_wu8Q" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN unavailable_ok_zUDw" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>No active subscription / Device is not registered with any account / SIM Card Not Inserted</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">RID indicator is blinking red</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>When the device has no active subsription / cannot connect to any account / detect an inserted SIM card, the red RID indicator blinks rapidly every 5 seconds.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt red_gEJV undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt green_ISeN undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Flight is Ready to Start without Cloud Communication</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">STAT and GNSS indicators are green, the RID indicator is red lit</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>After a flight ends with cloud communication failure, the device returns to the 'Flight Ready' state. However, cloud connectivity remains unavailable, indicated by a solid red RID indicator.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt cyan_FA_d running_1_iFRX" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt cyan_FA_d running_2_UpqZ" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt cyan_FA_d running_3_Hw15" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Turning Off</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">Running cyan on all indicators</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>The device is performing shutdown tasks and will soon turn off. Please wait until it finishes. If the device's cellular signal is poor or the configuration has changed, powering off might take up to one minute.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt undefined burst_1_InIx" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt undefined burst_2_k4CB" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt undefined burst_3_pNqS" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Updating Firmware / Reset to Factory Defaults in progress</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">Running rainbow on all indicators</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>The firmware on the device is being updated to the latest version / Reset to factory defaults is in progress. Please, do not turn off the&nbsp;device or disconnect it from the USB (if already connected). Wait for the update / reset to be finished.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt magenta_OUe8 undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt magenta_OUe8 undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt magenta_OUe8 undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Power Reset</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">All indicators are pink lit</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>Hold the button for 15 seconds to perform device power reset. All LED indicators will light up solid pink to indicate the power reset got executed.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt magenta_OUe8 countdown_1_pkzY" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt magenta_OUe8 countdown_2_Wnnj" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt magenta_OUe8 countdown_3_rX8u" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Reset Settings to Factory Defaults</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">Pink indicators turn off sequentially</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>Immediately after the Power Reset, if the button remains held, the device enters a factory reset countdown. The LEDs turn off one by one during the countdown. To complete the Settings Factory Reset, continue holding the button until all LEDs turn off and the RGB animation begins. Once finished, the LEDs light up white for 1 second, and the device restarts with factory settings.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt white_tszl undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt white_tszl undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt white_tszl undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Device Recovery Mode</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">All indicators are white lit</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>The device has entered recovery mode. There are two situations when it might happen:</p>
<ol>
<li>Device encountered fatal error in the firmware and needs to be hard restarted (15 s button press).</li>
<li>You have plugged the recovery dongle inside EXT port. In recovery mode, you are able to update the device firmware via USB. To quit this mode, hold the button for 15 s.</li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt off_Z6d3 undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt red_gEJV undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt off_Z6d3 undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Unrecoverable Error</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">One of the indicators is red lit</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>An unrecoverable error happened on the device side. It might be caused by various reasons, from GNSS/LTE timeout to the unreachable cloud for Network Remote ID functionality. Please turn the&nbsp;device off and on with a button long press (2 s). If the problem persists, go to <a href="https://help.dronetag.com/dronetag-mini/troubleshooting">Troubleshooting</a>.</p></div></div></div>
<hr class="clear-divider">
<div class="ledIndication_btB9 hasDescription_HXXL" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="miniLedIndicator__C43 horizontal_rlYG" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">GNSS</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt off_Z6d3 undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">RID</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt red_gEJV five-flashes_cZdR" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div><div class="ledLabeled_Z5I1" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="ledLabel_jS_Z" bis_skin_checked="1">STAT</div><div class="led__fSG on_VxAt off_Z6d3 undefined" bis_skin_checked="1"></div></div></div><div class="description_t914" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="titleBlock_tohq" bis_skin_checked="1"><div class="expandBlock_jjUo" bis_skin_checked="1"><h3>Temporary Error</h3><button class="expandButton_Qixu"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="30" width="30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M11.9999 13.1714L16.9497 8.22168L18.3639 9.63589L11.9999 15.9999L5.63599 9.63589L7.0502 8.22168L11.9999 13.1714Z"></path></svg></button></div><p class="subtitle_beFF">One or more indicators are blinking red</p></div><div class="descriptionTextHidden_R0qP clickPropagationCancel" bis_skin_checked="1"><p>Some user-oriented actions may fail due to the unreadiness of the device or its components. For&nbsp;example, this can happen if you want to start flight before the GNSS/RID is fully prepared or if you're going to turn on the device when discharged. Please try to repeat the action once the&nbsp;device is in the proper state.</p></div></div></div>
